snippet.title: CAFE 0 ~The Sleeping Beast~ REMASTERED | Console Version Trailer
snippet.description:
Unravel the mystery where past and present intertwine! 
The visual novel CAFE 0 ~The Sleeping Beast~ REMASTERED is coming to Nintendo Switch™,PS5®, PS4®, XBOX and XBOX Series S | X on November 1st, 2024. 
Don’t forget to preorder or wishlist and be among the first to uncover the truth!

Official URL: https://cafe0.roseverte.net/beast/en/remastered

Nintendo Switch https://store-jp.nintendo.com/list/software/70010000085491.html
PlayStation®Store https://store.playstation.com/ja-jp/concept/10012131
